      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Completely off-topic: you should never use the constructor of <code>Integer</code>. It&#39;ll bypass the internal caching mechanism of the <code>Integer</code> class. Its use is also deprecated in newer Java versions. Use <code>Integer.valueOf(int)</code> instead."
